title.rendered: 6 Pack, Pfizer Chlorhexidine and Cetrimide Irrigation Solution 30ml tubes

content.rendered: Chlorhexidine Irrigation Solution 0.1% 30ml Ampoule is used for cleansing and irrigating the skin or wounds or to prepare the body before using a special tube to drain the bladder (catheter). It contains antiseptics that will help prevent infection.
